connection to spirit.

00:35:18.640 --> 00:35:21.590 align:middle line:84%
We've lost our
connection to source.

00:35:21.590 --> 00:35:26.060 align:middle line:84%
We've lost our connection to
the oneness of consciousness

00:35:26.060 --> 00:35:28.780 align:middle line:90%
